      section
        h2 Introduction
        p Welcome to FinTrack. Your privacy is important to us. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our app.

      section
        h2 Information We Collect
        p FinTrack collects limited data through Google APIs with the following permissions:
        ul
          li
            strong Profile Information:
            | We only access basic profile information (such as your name and email) using the "profile" and "openid" scopes.
          li
            strong Email Access:
            | We request read-only access to your Gmail using the "gmail.readonly" scope. This is solely to fetch transaction-related emails for tracking your expenses.
        
      section
        h2 How We Use Your Information
        p We use the information collected to:
        ul
          li Analyze your transactions for personal finance management.
          li Provide insights and summaries based on your spending patterns.
          li Improve the functionality and user experience of FinTrack.
        
      section
