      section
        h2 Third-Party Sharing
        p We do not share your data with any third-party services. The access to your Gmail and profile information is strictly used for personal finance tracking and management within the FinTrack app.

      section
        h2 Data Retention
        p We retain your data only as long as necessary for providing our services. You can revoke access at any time via your Google Account settings.

      section
        h2 Your Rights
        p You have the right to:
        ul
          li Access the information we have collected from you.
          li Request deletion of your data from our servers.
          li Revoke permissions granted to FinTrack at any time.

